Copy the following from nominal model:
salt2_lc_dispersion_scaling.dat  (100 A binning!)
salt2_color_dispersion.dat

The U-magerr floor is set to zero here, which is 
different than the 0.1 magerr floor in SALT2.Guy10.
In the JLA analsis, CFA3,CSP,SDSS UV region has no
additional UV error; however, a 0.1 UV-magerr is
added to CalanTololo, CFAI,CFAII, lowz.
